Class PasswordTextbox

  • java.lang.Object
    • guiSET.core.Control

              • guiSET.core.PasswordTextbox

  • public class PasswordTextbox
extends Textbox
    This is a textbox where all chars will be displayed with the passwordChar character. Copying (or cutting) text is not possible or better it will return a bunch of password chars. Pasting is enabled. DISCLAIMER: This class is not the least bit a really secure textbox as the content is stored in memory as a plain string.
